\v 23 Xi³ je³to⁴tjen⁴ntai¹ Pedro cao⁴ Juan, qui³con³-le⁴ mi²yo⁴-le⁴. Tsa³cˀe¹ na⁴jmi¹ jo³ qui³tso²-le⁴ cho⁴ta⁴ti¹tjon²-le⁴ na⁴ˀmi³ cao⁴ cho⁴ta⁴jchi¹nca³.
