\v 27 Herodes cao⁴ Poncio Pilato, cao⁴ cho⁴ta⁴ xi³ li² judío jin², cao⁴ na⁴xi⁴na³nta¹-le⁴ Israel, cjoa⁴qui²xi⁴ nca³ coan³xco¹ i⁴ na⁴xi⁴na³nta¹je³ co²ntran⁴-le⁴ Jesús ˀnti¹-li⁴ xi³ tsje³, xi³ tsa³cˀai²-lai⁴ cjoa⁴te¹xo³ma³.
