\v 29 Ntˀai⁴-vi⁴ntai⁴, Señor, cho¹tsen³-lai⁴ jo³-sˀin² nca³ chˀao³-sˀin² vˀe¹ne²-na³jin⁴. Cho¹xˀa¹ˀnte³-lai⁴ cho⁴ˀnta³-li⁴ nca³ tsi² tsa² ca²ta³fi²cja³ˀa¹ cjoa⁴jcon³ nca³ coi⁴nchja⁴ en¹-li⁴.
\v 30 Tjain³ ntsai⁴, jme¹-ni³ nca³ coan⁴nta³-si¹ni³ chˀin³. Choa⁴ cao⁴ cjoa⁴xcon¹ ca²ta³ma³ xi³ to⁴tˀa³tsˀe⁴ jan³ˀain¹-le⁴ Jesús ˀnti¹-li⁴ xi³ tsje³.
