\v 37 Cˀia⁴ nca³ je³ja³ˀa³to³ xo⁴cjoan³-ve⁴, ji³so¹tjen⁴ Judas, je² cho⁴ta⁴ galileo, je² ni⁴čhjin³ nca³ qui³sˀe³nta³ padrón. A³li² to⁴cˀoa⁴cji³ cho⁴ta⁴ na⁴xi⁴na³nta¹ xi³ je² qui³cao⁴. Cˀoa⁴-ti⁴ cˀen³ nca³ je². Nca³tsˀi³ xi³ je² qui³tˀa³-le⁴ ña³qui³ qui³tsao³va³.
\v 38 Ntˀai⁴-vi⁴ntai⁴ cˀoa⁴xin³-no³: Ca²ta³vˀe²-la²no³, to⁴cˀoa⁴-la²sˀin² ti⁴ca³tio¹ je² cho⁴ta⁴xˀin⁴-vi⁴. Je² cjoa⁴ xi³ tji¹nta³-le⁴, cˀoa⁴ je² xa¹-vi⁴ tsa² tsˀe⁴ cho⁴ta⁴xˀin⁴, si⁴²cha³.
\v 39 To⁴nca³ tsa² tsˀe⁴ Ni³na¹ ni¹, a³li²coi³ coan⁴-no³ jo³ si⁴cao⁴³. Ti⁴coi²ntao⁴³ yao³-no³ tsa² coi³ ni⁴čhjin³ coi⁴yo³ta²ja³-lao⁴³ Ni³na¹.
\v 40 Cho⁴ta⁴junta tjio¹jin³con³ cao⁴ je² Gamaliel. Qui³nchja⁴-le⁴ pa²stro⁴. Cˀia⁴ nca³ je³tsa³ca¹-le⁴, chˀao³-sˀin² tsa³cˀe¹ne²-le⁴ nca³ tsi² tsa² cao⁴ jan³ˀain¹-le⁴ Jesús coi⁴nchja⁴. Cˀoa⁴ qui³sca³ni¹ntai¹-ˀni³.
