\v 5 Ni³na¹ li²coi³ qui³tsjoa³cjoa⁴tjao²-le⁴ na³nqui³, ni⁴ sa³ˀnta³ jña³ nca³ coa⁴sen² jnco³ ntso⁴co⁴. To⁴nca³ Ni³na¹ qui³tsjoa³ tsˀoa³ nca³ tsjoa¹-le⁴ xi³ ti⁴tsˀe⁴-ni³, cao⁴ xi³ tsˀe⁴ ntje⁴-le⁴ xi³ scan³-le⁴ nca³ je² cjoa⁴ˀai¹, nta³ tsa² cje³ tjin¹-jin²le⁴ ˀnti¹.
