\v 32 Cˀoa⁴coan³ nca³ Pedro tsa³cˀa³mjen³son² nca³tsˀi³ cho⁴ta⁴-le⁴ Cristo. Cˀoa⁴-ti⁴ ja³ˀai³con²-le⁴ je² cho⁴ta⁴-le⁴ Cristo xi³ tjio¹ ya⁴ Lida.
