\v 35 Ña³qui³ cˀoa⁴-sˀin² tsa³ca³co³-no³ nca³ cjai¹nca³ to⁴ma³chjen¹ nca³ cˀoa⁴-sˀin² ni²xa¹ nca³ coi⁴ncha³coa⁴² xi³ tjio¹mˀen³, nca³ si⁴cja³ˀai³tsjen³² je² en¹-le⁴ Nai³-na¹ Jesús xi³ qui³tso²: To⁴nqui²sa⁴ nta³-ni¹ nca³ cˀoe⁴² cao⁴-ni³ tsa² nca³ chjoe¹.
