\v 37 Cˀia⁴ nca³ je³ti¹si¹cˀa³sˀen³ ya⁴³ cuartel, Pablo cˀoi⁴qui³tso²-le⁴ je² xi³ nca³jco⁴-le⁴ so³nta²do⁴: A³ cˀoai⁴ˀnte³-nai¹³ nca³ cjoa²cao⁴ i⁴tse¹-le²³. Cˀoa⁴ je² qui³tso²: A³ ma³-li² en¹ griego?
