\v 22 Je² Félix cjai¹nca³ nta³ tjin¹jin³-le⁴ jo³-sˀin² ma³cjain¹-le⁴ je² cho⁴ta⁴-vi⁴ xi³ ntia⁴²tˀa³xin²-le⁴ Ni³na¹ fi²tˀa³-le⁴. Coi³ cjoa⁴ qui³sco³ya³cao⁴cjoa⁴ je² cjoa⁴-ve⁴ cˀia⁴ nca³ je³qui³nčhˀoe¹ nca³yi³je³ je² en¹-vi⁴ cˀoi⁴qui³tso²: Cˀia⁴ nca³ cjoa⁴ˀai¹jen³ je² Lisias xi³ nca³jco⁴-le⁴ so³nta²do⁴, cˀia⁴ cjoe⁴scoe³ je² cjoa⁴ xo⁴tjin¹-no³vi⁴.
